What Tau adds

Contract DSL + digests (codex/contracts/{schema.json,engine.py}) to describe work with price/deadline/virtue floor.

Autonomous agent runner + background scheduler (codex/agents/{runner.py,scheduler.py}) that executes tasks and writes ledger entries.

Task policy guard (codex/policy/{rules.json,engine.py}) allow/deny + virtue floor.

Payout-aware ledger (codex/economy/ledger.py) records energy, clarity, virtue, revenue, note.

Governance hooks (codex/governance/{roles.json,vote.py}) for simple approvals.

REST API + UI (dashboard/{api.py,ui.html} on port 8806) to submit contracts and view ledger.

Dockerfile and CI workflow (deploy/Dockerfile, .github/workflows/tau_ci.yml).

Manifest: per-file SHA-256 in codex/manifest.json.


Quick start

# Run API (port 8806)
python3 dashboard/api.py

# Submit a contract
curl -s -X POST localhost:8806/api/submit \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d @scripts/example_contract.json | jq

# View last ledger entries
curl -s localhost:8806/api/ledger | jq

